refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
public array Imagick::getImageArtifacts stringpattern"*"
Returns an associative array of image artifacts whose names match the given pattern. Artifacts are internal, named pieces of metadata attached to an image that pass extra options to specific ImageMagick operations; they are not written to the output file.

&reftitle.parameters;
pattern
A shell-style glob pattern matched against artifact names. The default "*" matches every artifact.
